{
  "expireTime": 9007200849225659000,
  "key": "transformer-remark-markdown-html-257cb1d419764686cb80a11a28cfa8ee-gatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-external-linksgatsby-remark-prismjs-",
  "val": "<h1>Why would I want to build this?</h1>\n<p>Not only will you achieve a fully customisable automation workflow, you will realise that you can automate anything.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Automation is fun</li>\n<li>No third party companies tracking your location</li>\n<li>No coding required</li>\n<li>Learn a new skill</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>How do I build this?</h1>\n<h2>Install Tasker</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the Google Play store and search for Tasker or click on this link</li>\n<li>Tap Buy / Install</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Build the automation</h1>\n<h2>Open Tasker</h2>\n<p>Now that you have installed Tasker, go ahead and open the app. You will be presented with a blank screen as shown below.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/25ab3578323c0ed0a4fb5604a78b19f2/16038/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/25ab3578323c0ed0a4fb5604a78b19f2/9a1e7/1.jpg 250w,\n/static/25ab3578323c0ed0a4fb5604a78b19f2/10bbb/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/25ab3578323c0ed0a4fb5604a78b19f2/16038/1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/25ab3578323c0ed0a4fb5604a78b19f2/44838/1.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Add a profile</h2>\n<p>Ensuring you are on the Profile tab, click on the ➕button in the bottom right corner. Upon clicking the ➕button you will see a context menu as shown below. Click on the <strong>Event</strong> option.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/547872ce6ba05adfbe66b6ec1bb19f01/16038/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/547872ce6ba05adfbe66b6ec1bb19f01/9a1e7/2.jpg 250w,\n/static/547872ce6ba05adfbe66b6ec1bb19f01/10bbb/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/547872ce6ba05adfbe66b6ec1bb19f01/16038/2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/547872ce6ba05adfbe66b6ec1bb19f01/44838/2.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Select Event Category</h2>\n<p>You will now be presented with the below modal. Then click on the option <strong>Phone</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 771px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/9a68a0c492ba83acb7f898ec7268949f/53eec/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9a68a0c492ba83acb7f898ec7268949f/9a1e7/3.jpg 250w,\n/static/9a68a0c492ba83acb7f898ec7268949f/10bbb/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/9a68a0c492ba83acb7f898ec7268949f/53eec/3.jpg 771w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Select Phone Event</h2>\n<p>Once you have clicked on the <strong>Phone</strong> option in the above step, you will be presented with the below modal. Now click on <strong>Received Text</strong> option.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/b538bca38cc37c2003e74194e6ef8562/16038/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b538bca38cc37c2003e74194e6ef8562/9a1e7/4.jpg 250w,\n/static/b538bca38cc37c2003e74194e6ef8562/10bbb/4.jpg 500w,\n/static/b538bca38cc37c2003e74194e6ef8562/16038/4.jpg 1000w,\n/static/b538bca38cc37c2003e74194e6ef8562/44838/4.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Event Edit</h2>\n<p>You will now be presented with this form.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/f04669c0336925ff2e03658014d3e3f1/16038/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f04669c0336925ff2e03658014d3e3f1/9a1e7/5.jpg 250w,\n/static/f04669c0336925ff2e03658014d3e3f1/10bbb/5.jpg 500w,\n/static/f04669c0336925ff2e03658014d3e3f1/16038/5.jpg 1000w,\n/static/f04669c0336925ff2e03658014d3e3f1/44838/5.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Set Content</h2>\n<p>Now is the time you will need to choose a trigger word. In this example I’m using <strong>#TRIGGER</strong>. Set the content to the trigger message you want.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/fd26771b9dc94e311f80e06e6b1279a3/16038/6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd26771b9dc94e311f80e06e6b1279a3/9a1e7/6.jpg 250w,\n/static/fd26771b9dc94e311f80e06e6b1279a3/10bbb/6.jpg 500w,\n/static/fd26771b9dc94e311f80e06e6b1279a3/16038/6.jpg 1000w,\n/static/fd26771b9dc94e311f80e06e6b1279a3/44838/6.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Click Back</h2>\n<p>Once you have set the content, click the ⬅ arrow button in the top left.</p>\n<h2>Add New Task</h2>\n<p>After clicking the ⬅ arrow button, you will see the below screen with <strong>New Task</strong>. Click on the ➕button.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/c0fdde6d67d360f5b8fdf9fcb1081061/16038/7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c0fdde6d67d360f5b8fdf9fcb1081061/9a1e7/7.jpg 250w,\n/static/c0fdde6d67d360f5b8fdf9fcb1081061/10bbb/7.jpg 500w,\n/static/c0fdde6d67d360f5b8fdf9fcb1081061/16038/7.jpg 1000w,\n/static/c0fdde6d67d360f5b8fdf9fcb1081061/44838/7.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Then input a task name, for this example I have used <strong>Send Location</strong>. Then click on the ✔️button.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/6026d7b3cea9fe3fe65dfd4b17b3fe63/16038/8.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6026d7b3cea9fe3fe65dfd4b17b3fe63/9a1e7/8.jpg 250w,\n/static/6026d7b3cea9fe3fe65dfd4b17b3fe63/10bbb/8.jpg 500w,\n/static/6026d7b3cea9fe3fe65dfd4b17b3fe63/16038/8.jpg 1000w,\n/static/6026d7b3cea9fe3fe65dfd4b17b3fe63/44838/8.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now you will be presented with the below screen.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"9\"\n        title=\"9\"\n        src=\"/static/4f4bf073ecc560ff812660d1d988abe2/16038/9.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4f4bf073ecc560ff812660d1d988abe2/9a1e7/9.jpg 250w,\n/static/4f4bf073ecc560ff812660d1d988abe2/10bbb/9.jpg 500w,\n/static/4f4bf073ecc560ff812660d1d988abe2/16038/9.jpg 1000w,\n/static/4f4bf073ecc560ff812660d1d988abe2/44838/9.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Click on the ➕button.</p>\n<h2>Select Action Category</h2>\n<p>After clicking on the ➕button you will be presented with the below modal. Scroll down and click on the <strong>Location</strong> option.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 771px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/53eec/10.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/9a1e7/10.jpg 250w,\n/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/10bbb/10.jpg 500w,\n/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/53eec/10.jpg 771w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Select Location Action</h2>\n<p>Now select the <strong>Get Location v2</strong> option in the below modal.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"11\"\n        title=\"11\"\n        src=\"/static/07662115c790981807e501dcc34ce1b3/16038/11.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/07662115c790981807e501dcc34ce1b3/9a1e7/11.jpg 250w,\n/static/07662115c790981807e501dcc34ce1b3/10bbb/11.jpg 500w,\n/static/07662115c790981807e501dcc34ce1b3/16038/11.jpg 1000w,\n/static/07662115c790981807e501dcc34ce1b3/44838/11.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>After clicking on the <strong>Get Location v2</strong> option, you will be presented with the below screen.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 771px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"12\"\n        title=\"12\"\n        src=\"/static/9bfc47364e50435663d56b5a954eea87/53eec/12.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9bfc47364e50435663d56b5a954eea87/9a1e7/12.jpg 250w,\n/static/9bfc47364e50435663d56b5a954eea87/10bbb/12.jpg 500w,\n/static/9bfc47364e50435663d56b5a954eea87/53eec/12.jpg 771w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can ignore this and click the ⬅ arrow button. Now you will see one task has been added.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"13\"\n        title=\"13\"\n        src=\"/static/5bc464e38cca8a2a5f7eb7cc76ef39a2/16038/13.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5bc464e38cca8a2a5f7eb7cc76ef39a2/9a1e7/13.jpg 250w,\n/static/5bc464e38cca8a2a5f7eb7cc76ef39a2/10bbb/13.jpg 500w,\n/static/5bc464e38cca8a2a5f7eb7cc76ef39a2/16038/13.jpg 1000w,\n/static/5bc464e38cca8a2a5f7eb7cc76ef39a2/44838/13.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1>Add New Task</h1>\n<p>Now we need to add the task to send the SMS message. Click on the ➕button in the bottom right. This time we want to pick <strong>Phone</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 771px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"14\"\n        title=\"14\"\n        src=\"/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/53eec/14.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/9a1e7/14.jpg 250w,\n/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/10bbb/14.jpg 500w,\n/static/b821a19c268a1b94f0437fe0774f2f77/53eec/14.jpg 771w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Select Phone Option</h2>\n<p>Now select the Send SMS option.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 771px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"15\"\n        title=\"15\"\n        src=\"/static/d42ee4c71ed76c82c9ed06a2ad3c67a0/53eec/15.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d42ee4c71ed76c82c9ed06a2ad3c67a0/9a1e7/15.jpg 250w,\n/static/d42ee4c71ed76c82c9ed06a2ad3c67a0/10bbb/15.jpg 500w,\n/static/d42ee4c71ed76c82c9ed06a2ad3c67a0/53eec/15.jpg 771w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Set Number &#x26; Message</h2>\n<p>Now set the number to <strong>%SMSRF</strong> and set the message to <strong>%gl<em>map</em>url</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 771px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"16\"\n        title=\"16\"\n        src=\"/static/ba8ea84949f72c29ad8e053dd5491c55/53eec/16.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ba8ea84949f72c29ad8e053dd5491c55/9a1e7/16.jpg 250w,\n/static/ba8ea84949f72c29ad8e053dd5491c55/10bbb/16.jpg 500w,\n/static/ba8ea84949f72c29ad8e053dd5491c55/53eec/16.jpg 771w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Click Back</h2>\n<p>Now click on the ⬅ arrow button in the top left. You will then see we have two tasks showing.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"17\"\n        title=\"17\"\n        src=\"/static/22fcc1fb1b9dfb48cf03f8241b5bba2a/16038/17.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/22fcc1fb1b9dfb48cf03f8241b5bba2a/9a1e7/17.jpg 250w,\n/static/22fcc1fb1b9dfb48cf03f8241b5bba2a/10bbb/17.jpg 500w,\n/static/22fcc1fb1b9dfb48cf03f8241b5bba2a/16038/17.jpg 1000w,\n/static/22fcc1fb1b9dfb48cf03f8241b5bba2a/44838/17.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Click Back</h2>\n<p>Now click the ⬅ arrow button again. You will see the completed workflow.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 207.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"18\"\n        title=\"18\"\n        src=\"/static/e6286aa14a988c9a9312d578d68d141e/16038/18.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e6286aa14a988c9a9312d578d68d141e/9a1e7/18.jpg 250w,\n/static/e6286aa14a988c9a9312d578d68d141e/10bbb/18.jpg 500w,\n/static/e6286aa14a988c9a9312d578d68d141e/16038/18.jpg 1000w,\n/static/e6286aa14a988c9a9312d578d68d141e/44838/18.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now click on the ✔️button next to the magnifying glass to save the changes. Once you’ve done that, click on the ellipsis (…) button in the top right and click on <strong>Enable Tasker</strong>.</p>\n<h2>Done</h2>\n<p>You have now successfully built the automation to handle the SMS trigger which will send the location of the device.</p>\n<h1>Test the automation</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Open your SMS app.</li>\n<li>Send yourself a text message with the trigger message you chose i.e. #TRIGGER</li>\n<li>You should receive a text from yourself with the trigger message.</li>\n<li>You should then receive a text with a Google Maps link of the location of your device.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"19.gif\"></p>\n<p>You will now be able to send your device a SMS with the trigger message from any mobile phone.</p>\n<p><em>Remember not to share the trigger word with anyone, otherwise they will be able to track you too!</em></p>\n<h1>Conclusion</h1>\n<p>In this blog post, we covered how to build automation that when a SMS message is received with a trigger word, it automatically replies with the location of the device. This can be used for tracking your mobile phone if you’ve lost it or someone has stolen it.</p>\n<p>This was just one example of what you can automate with Tasker for Android. The possibilities are endless. Go and automate something!</p>\n<p>If you want me to write up an article on how to automate something specific, leave a comment and let me know.</p>\n<h1>Original Presentation 👇</h1>\n<p>This talk was originally presented at <a href=\"https://tray.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tray.io</a> by <a href=\"https://www.thomaschaplin.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thomas Chaplin</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/CB28ogVLW5o\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">YouTube Video</a></p>"
}
